import React from 'react';
import { Navbar, Nav, Container, Col, Row, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';
import './Header.css';

export default function Header() {
    return (
        <header>
            <Navbar className='py-3' bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="sm" sticky="top">
                <Container className='ms-10'>
                    <Navbar.Brand className='nav-brand' href="#home">ArchHealthy</Navbar.Brand>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="ms-5">
                        <Col>
                            <Nav.Link  href="#home">Best Offers</Nav.Link>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Your orders</Nav.Link>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Cart</Nav.Link>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Login</Nav.Link>
                        </Col>
                    </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </header>
    )
}
